going to be one of our strategic platform for the pricing and analytics world. So I

00:04:21.359 --> 00:04:26.559
wanted to see the product getting evolved. And again, that's going to be a completely

00:04:26.559 --> 00:04:31.000
different experience in terms of again, bringing the maturity. And also, you know,

